Package: poly-c60-profile-smart-speaker
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, alsa-utils
Description: C60 device profile: smart speaker (voice appliance)
 Selects the smart-speaker role for the Polycom Trio C60 mic array + speaker. Ships the audio baseline (alsa-utils); the voice application itself is not yet built, so apply-config boots this role to a serviceable console until a poly-smart-speaker.service is present. Placeholder role, honestly incomplete. See polycom_dev/PROFILES-PLAN.md.
